COMMUTER

The 16-passenger Britten-Norman "Trislander" pictured on the front is the latest addition
to the Stol Air Commuter fleet. Stol Air, the first airline in the United States to fly the roomy
and comfortable "Trislander," will be flying this exciting airplane in their new route between
Oakland and San Francisco.
